          <p><strong>Content + Local + social handled for you:</strong> theStacc Bundle ($167/mo). <strong>Autonomous on-page fixes:</strong> Search Atlas OTTO ($99/mo). <strong>Strategy + done-for-you:</strong> Adaptify ($499/mo). <strong>DIY suite with rank tracking:</strong> SE Ranking ($65/mo). <strong>Budget content autopilot:</strong> SEO Bot ($59/mo) or Outrank ($49/mo).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Cancel the retainer — keep the output.</h4>
            <p>theStacc Bundle handles SEO articles, Google Business posts, and social — auto-published. <strong>$167/mo all-in</strong> vs $3,000/mo for the agency doing the same scope.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">See a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · 15-min walkthrough</span>
          </div>
