          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — match a typical $3K/mo agency package: 6 articles, GBP posts, on-page fixes, monthly report.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — output shipped, indexing rate, ranking lift, total cost.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $2,140 across 10 tools, Mar–May 2026.</li>
        </ul>

